1
00:00:03,545 --> 00:00:04,838
(Kaho) Also to Yukiya-kun⸺

2
00:00:04,921 --> 00:00:07,298
I want you to look forward and live your life properly.

3
00:00:07,382 --> 00:00:11,052
(Yukiya) I will destroy them in order to live properly.

4
00:00:11,761 --> 00:00:15,306
(Erika) With this, both in name and reality⸺

5
00:00:16,558 --> 00:00:19,436
I became everything to the Ise family.

6
00:01:15,033 --> 00:01:16,618
 (Masayuki) Get out of the way

7
00:01:17,619 --> 00:01:18,870
Who is it anyway? you

8
00:01:18,953 --> 00:01:20,121
 (Guardian) Outsiders are not allowed in.

9
00:01:20,205 --> 00:01:21,873
 (Masayuki) You must be an outsider!

10
00:01:21,956 --> 00:01:23,249
(Security) I can't pass you through.

11
00:01:23,333 --> 00:01:24,167
(Masayuki) That's all you can say.

12
00:01:24,250 --> 00:01:25,084
 (Security) Please go home.

13
00:01:25,168 --> 00:01:26,086
(Masayuki) That's all you can say, too.

14
00:01:26,169 --> 00:01:28,505
(Erika) Lively since the morning

15
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:31,424
No outsiders are allowed to enter.

16
00:01:31,508 --> 00:01:33,468
- (Masayuki) Hey! - (Erika) Fufu...

17
00:01:35,386 --> 00:01:36,805
(Fuyu) Wife

18
00:01:41,059 --> 00:01:42,894
What did you just say?

19
00:01:45,772 --> 00:01:48,650
Instead of “Yeah?”

20
00:01:48,733 --> 00:01:50,985
How to call it now

21
00:01:54,781 --> 00:01:56,282
Hey!

22
00:01:57,158 --> 00:01:59,536
I should have become the owner of this place.

23
00:01:59,619 --> 00:02:00,620
(Masayuki) Who do you think I am?

24
00:02:00,703 --> 00:02:02,038
(Security) I cannot pass you on.

25
00:02:02,122 --> 00:02:03,998
I'm sorry

26
00:02:04,082 --> 00:02:06,709
(Masayuki) Stop it, don't press it! Wow!

27
00:02:06,793 --> 00:02:09,462
Well, it's noisy outside, so do something about it.

28
00:02:09,546 --> 00:02:11,923
(Masayuki) He said I was the owner of this house!

29
00:02:12,006 --> 00:02:13,633
I got it

30
00:02:15,635 --> 00:02:20,598
(Masayuki) Woohoo... Erika! It's me! I'm back!

31
00:02:21,516 --> 00:02:26,229
(♪ Audio: Classic)

32
00:02:39,242 --> 00:02:40,827
(Masayuki) Let go! Hey!

33
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:44,289
(Masayuki) Come on! Uuuuuuuuck...

34
00:02:44,372 --> 00:02:45,623
(Security) Please go home.

35
00:02:45,707 --> 00:02:50,920
So... I am the master of this Ise family.

36
00:02:51,004 --> 00:02:55,008
Masayuki Ise is the eldest son of this family!

37
00:02:55,091 --> 00:02:59,262
This house and this land are all mine!

38
00:02:59,345 --> 00:03:00,930
- (Security) Um! -(Masayuki) Hmm...

39
00:03:01,014 --> 00:03:02,891
- (Security) Hmph! -(Masayuki) There you are... You...

40
00:03:02,974 --> 00:03:04,851
What is it, you! This... uh...

41
00:03:04,934 --> 00:03:07,437
(Security) Don't be careless! (sound of door opening)

42
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:13,610
(♪ Audio: Classic)

43
00:03:15,028 --> 00:03:18,948
Could you please not make a loud noise? Miyabi wakes up

44
00:03:20,408 --> 00:03:22,452
...Don't do it! Hmm!

45
00:03:22,535 --> 00:03:25,496
Erika! Hey Miyabi! Woohoo...

46
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:29,709
Hey! Ha... let go! Let go, hey!

47
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:35,965
(baby crying)

48
00:03:43,348 --> 00:03:45,350
‪♪～

49
00:04:41,114 --> 00:04:43,449
‪～♪

50
00:04:48,871 --> 00:04:50,290
(Yukiya) Erika

51
00:04:50,373 --> 00:04:51,332
(sound of glass breaking)

52
00:04:54,252 --> 00:04:55,545
you…

53
00:04:58,423 --> 00:05:01,050
(shutter sound)

54
00:05:02,343 --> 00:05:04,137
what do you want?

55
00:05:37,003 --> 00:05:38,254
(Female) Since you came⸺

56
00:05:38,338 --> 00:05:40,214
The Ise family continues to suffer misfortune.

57
00:05:40,298 --> 00:05:42,008
(Male) The mastermind behind his father's murder...?

58
00:05:42,091 --> 00:05:43,384
(Female) Chairperson from the beginning⸺

59
00:05:43,468 --> 00:05:45,053
Wasn't that what you were aiming for?

60
00:05:49,807 --> 00:05:52,727
(Kyoko) I have no intention of handing over the Ise family to you.

61
00:05:53,895 --> 00:05:56,773
(Kyoko) This house belongs to Masa-kun.

62
00:05:57,982 --> 00:05:59,067
(Erika) Huh?

63
00:06:00,485 --> 00:06:02,779
Even though you jumped at me

64
00:06:03,321 --> 00:06:05,823
When Masa-kun was in trouble⸺

65
00:06:05,907 --> 00:06:08,034
What is “chairman”?

66
00:06:08,117 --> 00:06:10,495
What is an “inauguration ceremony”?

67
00:06:12,455 --> 00:06:14,624
Mother-in-law, calm down

68
00:06:14,707 --> 00:06:16,709
What happened suddenly?

69
00:06:16,793 --> 00:06:20,713
For now... this is your best bet.

70
00:06:25,134 --> 00:06:27,929
If you say so, it sounds good.

71
00:06:30,515 --> 00:06:34,060
When you came to my house using Miyabi as an excuse⸺

72
00:06:34,143 --> 00:06:35,978
You looked bad.

73
00:06:37,021 --> 00:06:40,358
No one seemed to notice though⸺

74
00:06:40,441 --> 00:06:43,069
It's obvious to me

75
00:06:46,697 --> 00:06:49,158
It's the best day ever

76
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:54,705
It's best not to know anything

77
00:06:57,834 --> 00:06:59,377
what?

78
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:05,675
You seem to be misunderstanding something⸺

79
00:07:05,758 --> 00:07:10,346
Marrying into the Ise family means becoming a member of this family.

80
00:07:11,472 --> 00:07:13,099
Even if that is⸺

81
00:07:14,934 --> 00:07:18,479
Even if it is an inconvenient and cold prison⸺

82
00:07:21,899 --> 00:07:26,571
Your role is to fulfill your role as the chairman's wife.

83
00:07:31,659 --> 00:07:32,827
(Erika) Huh...

84
00:07:34,245 --> 00:07:36,080
poor person

85
00:07:38,875 --> 00:07:43,588
Is it the era? Or ability?

86
00:07:43,671 --> 00:07:46,799
Ha... fate?

87
00:07:51,804 --> 00:07:53,764
For me⸺

88
00:07:54,473 --> 00:07:58,561
This is a very interesting place, mother-in-law.

89
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:05,026
It's like a magical castle where dreams come true.

90
00:08:06,569 --> 00:08:07,820
Huh?

91
00:08:08,654 --> 00:08:12,200
Even if it's an inconvenient and cold prison for you⸺

92
00:08:13,326 --> 00:08:17,288
A paradise full of hope for me

93
00:08:21,167 --> 00:08:23,085
Hoora

94
00:08:24,795 --> 00:08:27,632
It's not what I said

95
00:08:27,715 --> 00:08:30,635
Masa-kun, it’s not what mom said.

96
00:08:30,718 --> 00:08:33,429
How did you end up with this?

97
00:08:35,765 --> 00:08:39,894
good? This isn't your paradise

98
00:08:39,977 --> 00:08:41,729
Don't say something stupid!

99
00:08:43,814 --> 00:08:47,944
This is Masa-kun's house

100
00:08:48,027 --> 00:08:51,239
this is our family home

101
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,702
I…

102
00:08:58,746 --> 00:09:02,083
I can do anything for that child

103
00:09:03,668 --> 00:09:06,003
For those of you who think of children as nothing more than a gift⸺

104
00:09:06,087 --> 00:09:07,838
I guess you don't understand.

105
00:09:13,719 --> 00:09:17,473
I don't have a single regret.

106
00:09:24,605 --> 00:09:29,527
(Erika) I feel sorry for you, mistaking such constraints for love.

107
00:09:30,486 --> 00:09:31,779
Mother...

108
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:36,576
(Erika) You must have had a poor life.

109
00:09:37,702 --> 00:09:38,995
Mother!

110
00:10:16,866 --> 00:10:18,159
(Erika) This time⸺

111
00:10:18,326 --> 00:10:24,248
Since I became the chairman due to the incident involving my husband Masayuki⸺

112
00:10:24,332 --> 00:10:27,626
We have received a variety of feedback on SNS.

113
00:10:29,003 --> 00:10:31,005
Words of encouragement⸺

114
00:10:31,839 --> 00:10:36,427
There are also words of concern for my health.

115
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:40,181
Thank you very much

116
00:10:40,723 --> 00:10:44,435
(shutter sound)

117
00:10:48,105 --> 00:10:51,859
But inside⸺

118
00:10:53,194 --> 00:10:55,988
Some critical content

119
00:10:57,865 --> 00:11:00,785
A title that is too heavy for me

120
00:11:01,952 --> 00:11:05,956
I think your criticism is valid.

121
00:11:06,791 --> 00:11:07,917
just⸺

122
00:11:09,668 --> 00:11:11,087
no matter what⸺

123
00:11:13,255 --> 00:11:15,883
There are some things that cannot be accepted

124
00:11:19,970 --> 00:11:21,389
I⸺

125
00:11:22,556 --> 00:11:24,767
I want the chairman's seat⸺

126
00:11:25,893 --> 00:11:30,731
It is believed that he may have approached the Ise family.

127
00:11:37,530 --> 00:11:39,532
That's all⸺

128
00:11:40,574 --> 00:11:45,454
I want to speak out loud and say “no”

129
00:11:49,542 --> 00:11:51,377
I'm just⸺

130
00:11:52,545 --> 00:11:56,507
She saved me from my ex-husband who repeatedly acted like a stalker⸺

131
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:58,342
To Masayuki...

132
00:11:58,426 --> 00:11:59,593
Huh?

133
00:12:00,302 --> 00:12:02,680
(Erika) I just want to return the favor.

134
00:12:03,973 --> 00:12:06,058
-(Woman) Huh? Seriously? -(Female) That's dangerous.

135
00:12:06,142 --> 00:12:08,352
-(Male) Erika-san, are you okay? -(Female) I'm too scared of stalkers.

136
00:12:08,436 --> 00:12:09,270
(Male) Shall I lie? I didn't know

137
00:12:09,353 --> 00:12:10,855
(Female) Masayuki Ise Points up

138
00:12:10,938 --> 00:12:13,023
(Erika) From harassment from my ex-husband⸺

139
00:12:14,942 --> 00:12:17,903
About Masayuki-san who protected me⸺

140
00:12:19,196 --> 00:12:21,115
This time I...

141
00:12:22,867 --> 00:12:24,410
I want to help

142
00:12:27,872 --> 00:12:32,042
What drives me now⸺

143
00:12:33,294 --> 00:12:34,754
like!

144
00:12:36,130 --> 00:12:37,798
That's it!

145
00:12:38,549 --> 00:12:41,427
(shutter sound)

146
00:12:54,023 --> 00:12:55,441
-(Reo) Is it delicious? -(kids) delicious

147
00:12:55,524 --> 00:12:57,067
- (Boy) It's delicious - (Reo) It's delicious.

148
00:13:00,738 --> 00:13:02,740
(Juna) Yukini says it's delicious.

149
00:13:04,492 --> 00:13:06,785
Yukini, what happened?

150
00:13:07,953 --> 00:13:08,829
(Yukiya) Yeah?

151
00:13:08,913 --> 00:13:10,831
Does your stomach hurt?

152
00:13:11,499 --> 00:13:13,751
(Yukiya) No, it's okay.

153
00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:17,797
Yukiya-san, I'm sorry.

154
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:20,758
I'm out of mayonnaise, so can I get some for you?

155
00:13:24,595 --> 00:13:25,804
ah…

156
00:13:31,602 --> 00:13:33,187
I'm going to go do some shopping.

157
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:37,066
-(Reo) Welcome.-(Children) Welcome.

158
00:13:52,873 --> 00:13:55,292
(Female) This photo tells the story of love.

159
00:14:28,325 --> 00:14:30,119
(sound of empty cans colliding)

160
00:14:49,305 --> 00:14:50,639
(throwing sound)

161
00:14:54,768 --> 00:14:57,313
why do you need me

162
00:14:59,773 --> 00:15:01,400
Will you kill me?

163
00:15:02,568 --> 00:15:04,737
I guess he came here to kill me.

164
00:15:05,946 --> 00:15:07,865
Damn... don't come!

165
00:15:09,199 --> 00:15:11,827
Even if you were thrown away, it's still a bummer.

166
00:15:12,453 --> 00:15:13,996
Huh?

167
00:15:14,079 --> 00:15:16,916
(Yukiya) Is this the end of the eldest son of the Ise family?

168
00:15:17,583 --> 00:15:18,959
(Masayuki) Huh...

169
00:15:20,294 --> 00:15:25,382
I can't stand being beaten by someone like you, who's kidding?

170
00:15:25,466 --> 00:15:28,052
I don't need you anymore

171
00:15:28,761 --> 00:15:30,929
It's as good as dead

172
00:15:33,932 --> 00:15:35,559
(sound of falling)

173
00:15:35,643 --> 00:15:38,520
(Masayuki) Uuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuu

174
00:15:38,604 --> 00:15:42,232
Haa... aaaaaa...

175
00:15:45,152 --> 00:15:47,112
Even if I go, I won't be able to meet you.

176
00:15:53,369 --> 00:15:56,080
Your goal is probably Erika anyway.

177
00:15:57,873 --> 00:16:02,002
Yes, that's me...

178
00:16:03,796 --> 00:16:05,923
Because it's the final revenge

179
00:16:07,966 --> 00:16:09,134
(Masayuki) Hehe...

180
00:16:10,636 --> 00:16:11,971
Huh...

181
00:16:15,474 --> 00:16:17,476
You look like an idiot.

182
00:16:18,852 --> 00:16:20,270
us

183
00:16:23,565 --> 00:16:26,735
We were both fooled by that woman.

184
00:16:28,028 --> 00:16:29,279
Huh...

185
00:16:31,615 --> 00:16:36,286
It's all about him, including my father.

186
00:16:41,375 --> 00:16:43,043
Ah yes

187
00:16:51,844 --> 00:16:53,262
(Masayuki) It's you

188
00:16:55,848 --> 00:16:58,308
What's good about a woman like that?

189
00:17:00,227 --> 00:17:01,562
Because I “made it”⸺

190
00:17:01,645 --> 00:17:04,606
There was also an heir, so we ended up together.

191
00:17:05,399 --> 00:17:06,567
Hehe...

192
00:17:07,151 --> 00:17:10,362
...Otherwise, it's just a game, a game.

193
00:17:14,324 --> 00:17:16,660
I shouldn't have done anything to my wife.

194
00:17:21,373 --> 00:17:22,916
But well...

195
00:17:24,126 --> 00:17:25,878
Your that⸺

196
00:17:27,129 --> 00:17:32,009
The look on his face when he was presented with the divorce papers was a masterpiece.

197
00:17:32,092 --> 00:17:38,932
laughter)

198
00:17:46,356 --> 00:17:47,566
Huh...

199
00:17:50,694 --> 00:17:52,029
Huh...

200
00:17:52,863 --> 00:17:54,490
It's okay now

201
00:17:55,783 --> 00:17:57,618
I don't care

202
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:03,248
You're not worth hating.

203
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:08,462
(Masayuki) Huh… hah hah…

204
00:18:10,172 --> 00:18:11,548
Hey

205
00:18:13,634 --> 00:18:14,593
(cough cough)

206
00:18:14,676 --> 00:18:16,720
Huh… hah…

207
00:18:16,804 --> 00:18:18,430
Huh...

208
00:18:19,973 --> 00:18:22,976
What do you want from Erika?

209
00:18:26,605 --> 00:18:28,982
to go to hell

210
00:18:34,905 --> 00:18:36,532
with me

211
00:18:38,742 --> 00:18:39,743
Haha...

212
00:18:48,043 --> 00:18:49,545
well…

213
00:18:51,421 --> 00:18:54,716
Does that mean Erika is yours after all?

214
00:20:38,528 --> 00:20:42,532
Until the end... I'm sorry

215
00:20:43,533 --> 00:20:44,785
Huh...

216
00:20:45,327 --> 00:20:46,703
Botchan

217
00:20:47,871 --> 00:20:49,706
I…

218
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:55,879
(Yukiya) Fuyu-san

219
00:21:10,435 --> 00:21:12,145
Thank you so far

220
00:21:17,109 --> 00:21:18,694
cry)

221
00:21:19,403 --> 00:21:20,404
(sound of door opening)

222
00:21:22,072 --> 00:21:23,073
(sound of door closing)

223
00:21:23,156 --> 00:21:27,160
cry)

224
00:22:04,489 --> 00:22:10,495
(heartbeat sound)

225
00:22:12,289 --> 00:22:14,124
(Erika) I thought you would come.

226
00:22:17,210 --> 00:22:20,255
It's really persistent

227
00:22:20,338 --> 00:22:23,425
It's no use trying to trick me

228
00:22:27,012 --> 00:22:29,181
It must be Yukiya-san anyway, right?

229
00:22:29,264 --> 00:22:31,600
feel ill

230
00:22:35,562 --> 00:22:37,397
What do you mean?

231
00:22:40,692 --> 00:22:42,944
Did your brother save you?

232
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:46,531
Don't be silly

233
00:22:47,991 --> 00:22:51,995
Huh... Because that's not it.

234
00:22:53,455 --> 00:22:57,584
How many times do I have to say, "Don't interfere with my happiness" before you understand?

235
00:22:59,669 --> 00:23:02,255
Is this what makes you happy?

236
00:23:04,049 --> 00:23:05,592
“Like this”?

237
00:23:07,094 --> 00:23:08,053
ah

238
00:23:10,347 --> 00:23:12,307
“It’s like this” Isn’t it boring?

239
00:23:15,936 --> 00:23:17,312
Could you please stop?

240
00:23:24,194 --> 00:23:26,154
Don't touch me again

241
00:23:27,572 --> 00:23:30,867
Even though I don't know how much I've been struggling

242
00:23:31,952 --> 00:23:33,370
Struggling?

243
00:23:36,832 --> 00:23:39,584
Even if you trample on someone's life⸺

244
00:23:39,668 --> 00:23:41,628
Being able to live a luxurious life⸺

245
00:23:41,711 --> 00:23:44,047
Is it happiness for you?

246
00:23:45,882 --> 00:23:51,638
Are you saying you don't care about other people in order to live an elegant life?

247
00:23:53,014 --> 00:23:56,184
what? A sermon?

248
00:24:14,995 --> 00:24:16,830
Not everyone

249
00:24:18,039 --> 00:24:19,791
all the time

250
00:24:22,419 --> 00:24:24,504
It's there in some places

251
00:24:26,631 --> 00:24:28,550
It's not there

252
00:24:30,927 --> 00:24:32,804
If so, just take it away.

253
00:24:34,181 --> 00:24:36,433
That's how I came about

254
00:24:37,726 --> 00:24:41,980
I've used them all...

255
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:47,527
That's what's happening

256
00:24:47,611 --> 00:24:49,529
There's no way it's allowed

257
00:24:49,613 --> 00:24:52,073
I'm not asking you to forgive me.

258
00:24:56,745 --> 00:24:59,414
That's not what I want

259
00:25:05,253 --> 00:25:06,713
It's lonely

260
00:25:14,512 --> 00:25:15,722
Yeah

261
00:25:17,015 --> 00:25:18,517
Of course, right?

262
00:25:20,018 --> 00:25:21,311
So what?

263
00:25:26,441 --> 00:25:29,819
Even Yukiya-san has been taking revenge for his loneliness.

264
00:25:32,239 --> 00:25:35,116
If you don't do that, you won't be able to move forward.

265
00:25:37,369 --> 00:25:39,120
What's the difference?

266
00:26:07,107 --> 00:26:08,858
Or...

267
00:26:11,027 --> 00:26:13,029
kill me⸺

268
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:16,825
Will I die too?

269
00:26:40,890 --> 00:26:42,726
I…

270
00:26:45,270 --> 00:26:47,480
I wanted to look back

271
00:26:49,441 --> 00:26:51,318
Fate and everything

272
00:27:03,705 --> 00:27:06,374
Because no one will save me

273
00:27:15,592 --> 00:27:17,469
You too will be happy soon⸺

274
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,972
don't forget about me

275
00:27:34,235 --> 00:27:35,945
(Yukiya) I'll put it simply.

276
00:27:39,783 --> 00:27:41,660
If you can do that⸺

277
00:27:43,536 --> 00:27:46,247
I'm already happy

278
00:27:55,423 --> 00:27:57,258
I'm looking for it.

279
00:27:58,551 --> 00:28:00,011
forever

280
00:28:01,763 --> 00:28:03,515
inside the memory

281
00:28:06,893 --> 00:28:08,436
just one

282
00:28:11,481 --> 00:28:14,109
There are times when I can say this

283
00:28:21,074 --> 00:28:22,575
Erika...

284
00:28:28,331 --> 00:28:31,084
When you smiled at me

285
00:28:35,296 --> 00:28:36,589
That...

286
00:28:43,471 --> 00:28:46,099
I still remember it many times

287
00:28:47,934 --> 00:28:50,478
I can't forget even if I want to forget

288
00:28:54,441 --> 00:28:55,942
At that time⸺

289
00:28:57,235 --> 00:28:58,903
I always⸺

290
00:29:01,698 --> 00:29:03,908
Always happy...

291
00:29:14,961 --> 00:29:16,337
I'm lonely

292
00:29:25,263 --> 00:29:27,557
What was that time?

293
00:29:29,017 --> 00:29:31,394
What was that smile about?

294
00:29:34,731 --> 00:29:36,900
He said "I love you"

295
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:44,991
Huh...

296
00:29:47,994 --> 00:29:49,704
Because

297
00:29:52,582 --> 00:29:54,751
...It wouldn't have started otherwise.

298
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:05,178
I became the person you are happy with

299
00:30:06,888 --> 00:30:09,849
Because if I didn't do that, I wouldn't have been able to fall in love with you.

300
00:30:13,144 --> 00:30:14,270
Huh...

301
00:30:17,190 --> 00:30:19,025
What kind of logic is that?

302
00:30:21,986 --> 00:30:24,656
Because my life only happens once

303
00:30:25,532 --> 00:30:26,866
(Yukiya) If so⸺

304
00:30:28,076 --> 00:30:29,786
What can I do?

305
00:30:32,539 --> 00:30:35,416
You just got fooled, right?

306
00:30:42,799 --> 00:30:43,800
Huh...

307
00:30:47,345 --> 00:30:48,721
oh dear…

308
00:30:50,765 --> 00:30:52,267
Maybe so

309
00:30:55,228 --> 00:30:56,688
surely

310
00:30:58,273 --> 00:31:00,692
If I had known, I wouldn't have approached you.

311
00:31:04,696 --> 00:31:05,864
but…

312
00:31:12,996 --> 00:31:15,248
For me at that time...

313
00:31:20,837 --> 00:31:22,839
you were everything

314
00:31:40,857 --> 00:31:42,358
Goodbye

315
00:31:55,288 --> 00:32:00,919
(Sound of door opening and closing)

316
00:32:18,645 --> 00:32:20,647
‪♪～

317
00:32:53,930 --> 00:32:55,390
(Yukiya as a child) Let's play together

318
00:32:59,519 --> 00:33:01,312
(Erika as a child) I don't need this.

319
00:33:02,730 --> 00:33:03,856
(Yukiya) Yeah?

320
00:33:06,567 --> 00:33:08,361
(Erika) I'm hungry.

321
00:33:42,645 --> 00:33:44,439
Good luck

322
00:34:19,390 --> 00:34:21,392
‪～♪

323
00:34:26,814 --> 00:34:29,650
(Hanaho) I'm still learning a lot of things⸺

324
00:34:30,693 --> 00:34:34,947
Cultivating herbs has always been a dream of mine, so I enjoy it every day.

325
00:34:35,031 --> 00:34:36,449
That's right

326
00:34:37,283 --> 00:34:39,619
Next time I'll bring it to Homohoya.

327
00:34:39,702 --> 00:34:41,287
thank you

328
00:34:54,717 --> 00:34:55,927
Hanaho-san

329
00:34:57,637 --> 00:35:01,599
The other day... I'm really sorry.

330
00:35:02,683 --> 00:35:05,394
You said it because you were thinking of me

331
00:35:08,147 --> 00:35:09,816
I don't care

332
00:35:11,776 --> 00:35:14,695
Yukiya-kun, even if just a little bit now⸺

333
00:35:14,779 --> 00:35:18,908
If you have more time to feel happy⸺

334
00:35:18,991 --> 00:35:22,453
That's fine, I'm happy too

335
00:35:30,211 --> 00:35:31,963
(The sound of a bell)

336
00:35:53,442 --> 00:35:54,694
-(Reo) Wait a minute.-(Yukiya) Do you want to eat a lot?

337
00:35:54,777 --> 00:35:56,696
- (Reo) Okay, yes, please - (Yukiya) Wait a minute.

338
00:35:56,779 --> 00:35:58,364
-(Yukiya) Do you know everyone's share? -(Girl) Yeah.

339
00:35:58,447 --> 00:36:00,867
-(Children) They should be there-(Yukiya) Okay... Hey.

340
00:36:00,950 --> 00:36:01,909
-(Reo) Um... -(Yukiya) Yes.

341
00:36:01,993 --> 00:36:02,869
-(Boy) Last one-(Boy) This is the end.

342
00:36:02,952 --> 00:36:04,829
-(Reo) I'll get it.-(Yukiya) Hey.

343
00:36:04,912 --> 00:36:07,790
-(Reo) Good job~ Good job-(Boy) Amazing

344
00:36:07,874 --> 00:36:09,542
Make sure to eat your vegetables too.

345
00:36:09,625 --> 00:36:12,587
(Juna) Raise it up and put your hands in it.

346
00:36:16,465 --> 00:36:20,136
Hey, we made friends at the park.

347
00:36:20,219 --> 00:36:22,597
(Yukiya) Hey, hello.

348
00:36:22,680 --> 00:36:25,474
(Boy) Hello (laughter)

349
00:36:25,558 --> 00:36:27,727
(Kina) Like this...

350
00:36:29,312 --> 00:36:31,063
here like this

351
00:36:35,276 --> 00:36:36,819
(Fuyu) You did well.

352
00:36:36,903 --> 00:36:37,987
(Miyabi) Yeah

353
00:36:45,620 --> 00:36:47,246
Master

354
00:36:48,331 --> 00:36:50,791
(Miyabi) Mama is home now.

355
00:36:52,835 --> 00:36:54,420
(Erika) Welcome back

356
00:36:54,503 --> 00:36:56,505
I'll give you this

357
00:37:05,932 --> 00:37:07,391
thank you

358
00:37:19,362 --> 00:37:20,696
Fufufufu…

359
00:37:21,239 --> 00:37:25,242
(sound of folding origami)
